title: Hotel Deal of the Week: CityNorth Hotel
text:
CityNorth Hotel, Gormanstown, Co. Meath
BOYNE VALLEY GOLF LINKS BREAK : €120pps – 2 nights Bed & Breakfast & Golf on three of the best golf courses on the East Coast - County Louth Golf Club Baltray, Bettystown & Laytown and Seapoint Golf Club.
Let the CityNorth Hotel arrange your tee times and transfers to and from the courses.
This is a midweek and weekend offer, valid September 1 to November 15, 2015.
www.citynorthhotel.com
